snippet.title: Miscreated: Environment Trailer - 4k Resolution!
snippet.description:
Click Here To Subscribe! ► http://bit.ly/JoinMiscreated

This is a 4k resolution video showing some of the environments in Miscreated.  It's part of what Crytek will be showing in their booth for the 2015 GDC (Game Developer's Conference).  Miscreated is available for purchase on Steam using the following Steam link.

Miscreated Media Outlets:
Official Website: http://miscreatedgame.com
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/299740
Facebook Page: http://facebook.com/miscreatedgame
Twitter: http://twitter.com/miscreatedgame
YouTube Channel: http://www.youtube.com/user/EntradaInteractive
Twitch.tv Stream: http://twitch.tv/miscreated
CryDev.net Discussion Thread: http://www.crydev.net/viewtopic.php?f=353&t=100397
